abloader is a plugin that allows the ray tracer Augenblick
to load RIB scenes. abloader can also be used by the RiCPP
frontend. abrib is a program that loads RIB and displays
its contents using Augenblick and GLUT.

For compilation:

Headers expected in /usr/local/include/Augenblick
libAugenblick.dylib in /usr/local/lib
Augenblick needs an additional directory /user/local/lib/Augenblick.

Augenblick is (c) by Oliver Abert, University of Koblenz
http://web.me.com/abert
